flowRoot.flowPara: Learn to make effective image descriptions:
Write your image description on the left, in the box marked "Image Description".
Check you image description against each of these reminders:

The boy stands with arms held up and looking up at the moon. He is wearing his red hat. In between the boy and the moon is a tree, and his blue hat is hanging from a tree branch so that it looks like it is resting on top of the moon. The moon is smiling.
